manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "backend"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "backend"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
actix-web = "4.3.1"
anyhow = "1.0.70"
delay_timer = "0.11.4"
diesel-enum = "0.1.0"
dotenvy = "0.15.7"
env_logger = "0.10.0"
json = "0.12.4"
log = "0.4.17"
scraper = "0.15.0"
serde_json = "1.0.95"
serde_qs = "0.12.0"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.24"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.1.13"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.diesel]
version = "2.0.3"
features = ["sqlite", "chrono"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.16"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.159"
features = ["derive"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "backend"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
